3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper uses the concept of observability and controllability, which are commonly used in the study of network dynamics. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the controllability and observability of trellises, which are concepts commonly used in control theory. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses the concept of product factorization, which is a common technique in machine learning for decomposing complex models into simpler ones.
